yeaaah i already like lost interest in this thing and ive only had it for like a few weeks, lol not suprised.  but yeah its been awhile, nonetheless.  ne who, last weekend was kinda weak but it was alright.  it mainly consisted of kevin and i going to his house like every night and trying to get people to do something, but no one really wanted to.  we almost got taylor to do something, but then she went to chris straights, so yea.  but we played at jakes last saturday, that was cool.  we got some stuff done.  jake got some flatwound strings for his bass, the sound really good.  im gonna buy some...but yea we played outside in his back yard, gave his neighbors a free show..lol

but yea, this week i got jesus camp! yessssss! its kinda cool this year, im in the seinor high group so im like kinda like a councelor, in the sense i dont really have to do the things i dont like to, such as crafts music and nature, which leaves rec, swim-which i dont do that lake is nasty-, and class, which i still have to do, but its not to bad.  its cool tho.  but jess is bein a bum and going to chicago on wednesday, so she cant go the whole week.  its all good tho.  my friend matt that i go with knows like everone at that camp beause he just got done with this like three week councelor training thing, so basically he talks to all the ladies and i get introduced.  lol but yeah jesus camp is cool this year.

this wednesday we got the badfish show at lupos.  kinda souped on that.  state radio and bad larry are there to so it should be pretty sweet, regan your fuckin going! its supposed to be pretty nuts there tho from what i hear from the last one.  lootsa naughty things goin on.  im a good kid tho dont worry abot me *thumbs up*.  

yeep, my parents are leavin for a vacation they arent taking me on on thursday.  but its only vermont who gives a shit...but yeah there stickin me with the grandma at home, idk its not to bad, its not like id throw a party ne way, i would worry about too much shit.  but yea i think ive written enough...my fingers hurt...not cool 

latadays
peace+
drew

heh, jess thinks fig newtons are gross, comment if you think otherwise. lol but yeah yesterday was werid. kevo calle me around noon and he came over with his guitar shit and we jammed for like a total of about 10 min, considering we were the only ones there and it was weird we stopped and went inside and watched the sox game.  w00t go yanks...then we spent all of about two hours calling people to try and go and do something, but that didnt really work out because either no one was home (lots a peeps are on vaca, makes me sad) or they didnt want to get off their ass (jess). lol so we ended up goin to applebees and shootin the shit for a bit. then we went to see the late show for the Wedding Crashers.  that movie was fucking awesome i want to go see i again.  soooo many one liners....ne who, we got back to my place round like 1230 ish and hit the hay.  got up round 11, and then met jamie and will at the beach round two. then, we (well more like jamie) decided to go to jamies grandparents house.  it was kinda cool but kinda weird.  idk we just like stayed in their basement and watched viva la bam, professional dodgeball, and the andy milonikis show (which i might add is absolutly halarious).  then jamies grandpa drove us to minigolf in ganset, then i came home and here i am! totally ready to go to work tomorrow! yeaaakinda.... but yeaah i didnt do ne thing like all week last week and i dont realy wanna do that again..it sucked

ne who, im out, lata days 
peace+
drew

so yeaaa...woke up this morning and went to work, that was cool i guess, i didnt have to stay in the wharehouse all day. got the buffalo chicken grinder for lunch, and by the way hell hes that is incredible.  lol yea but my boss (my uncle frank) cought me and ryan maning messin around like playin basketball with a volley ball and some trashcans, he kinda yelled at us and shit but its all good, its friday i dont really give a shit.  
yesterday was interesting...lol yea i was supposed to jam with the guys, but only connor could show so we had to cancel, leaving me with absolutly nothing to do.  therefore, on a whim, i decided to go for a bikeride to the beach in charlestown. it took me like 20 min to get there, and i probably only stayed long enough to walk up and down the beach and buy a soda then i left because i knew like absolutly no one there, so on my way back i pulled a forest gump and said "well i already came this far..."lol, so then i just kept going towards westerly and didnt stop till i got to stop and shop, i almost went to misquamicut beach, but i had to go to passin league later so i turned around. 
lol three hours later, when i got home, i learned that taylor was at misquamicut and she was like "damn kid i coulda came and picked you up use your phone." so the moral is ~ drew needs to get a fucking car

heyyy, yea i made a live journal...idk i had nothing to do today and like everyone has one so i figured id join the club i guess...so yea, i was gonna have band pratice today with the guys, i was all souped to write new stuff and shit, but only connor could come, bummer huh? so now im stuck here all day cuz like my whole family is at work..fun stuff..im so bored...

ne who, once the afternoon kicks in it wont be so bad, i have drum lessons at 4, then i have the passin league game thing at like 530 to 7, fun stuff... im thinkin about takin a bikeride to the beach or somethin i really wanna get outa the house its a nice day..but i may just sit on my ass untill 4 oclock comes around..we'll see i guess..

well that was fun i guess, lata days

peace+
drew
